Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.84,0:00:23.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.39,0:00:29.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.02,0:00:35.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:43.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然  充滿疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.66,0:00:51.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起度過每一天 直到將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.91,0:00:58.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流著眼淚  無法釋懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.63,0:01:09.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想請教  如何追回失去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:16.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.48,0:01:22.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.03,0:01:28.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.21,0:01:33.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把謎團解開吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.67,0:22:34.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.06,0:22:43.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此淒涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.02,0:22:50.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.48,0:22:59.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.12,0:23:08.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.50,0:23:16.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.76,0:23:26.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.85,0:23:35.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.25,0:00:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.79,0:00:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.35,0:00:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是山中競走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照字典的解釋就是迂迴登山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高利貸公司社長遭到殺害之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽連一輛幼稚園巴士翻車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並造成一名幼稚園兒童死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.12,0:02:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方目前已經逮捕教唆殺人的主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關消息表示 本案與雙方借貸有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.97,0:02:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行兇的人被稱為fox
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.06,0:02:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一名身份不詳的職業殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在逃亡當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而警方尚未掌握fox的正確行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.67,0:02:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖登山殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.14,0:02:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是半年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位無辜幼稚園兒童遇害的現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.77,0:02:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兇手fox的行蹤目前仍然沒有線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 有客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.77,0:02:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 小聲一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人都已經到這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧打擾真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我找到那個殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他不要殺你了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.27,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是個關西房屋仲介公司的東京分公司的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個月以前 我去接受一項健康檢查的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.44,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的胃潰瘍竟然被他們誤診成胃癌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當醫生和護士小姐把這件事情告訴我的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現自己竟然得了癌症真的是嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.15,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你就雇請了一個職業殺手來殺你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是fox
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在我發現這是誤會的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.61,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就利用對我能有幫助的各種關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過許多努力希望能跟fox取得聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.79,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是匯錢的方式或是聯絡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.33,0:04:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把發信人透過網路傳遞把消息儘量放出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我終於跟fox取得聯繫的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了一個月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.06,0:04:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果還要再聯絡到他的話也就沒有那麼容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.82,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才想到要來找我名偵探毛利小五郎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你說的是不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是騙我的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.42,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不相信我說的話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 快趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 他逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.87,0:05:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.96,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是先報警好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.25,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說這次的目標是我自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我雇用了殺手這是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕不會這樣善罷甘休的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不要警方插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶的賠償我會負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就接受好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個連警方都拿他束手無策的職業殺手fox
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.78,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我名偵探毛利小五郎去把他逮捕歸案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎麼去抓這個fox呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不知道他是怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我對fox開出了一個條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺我的話就要在我最喜歡的登山活動中動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種在山脊上面競走的活動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以登山活動為條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那剛才的槍擊又是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.07,0:06:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶旁邊實在太危險了 快點過來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再來多討論一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙一定有什麼內情才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.18,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天一早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個就到丹原山脈進行登山活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在山中競走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 柯南幫我照一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.59,0:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 這樣我們還沒爬山底片就會照光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你也跟我一起照吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你幫我們照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.27,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我們可不是來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個該知道怎麼做吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是為了要裝成一般的登山客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才特意跟著爸爸來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拍照也太奇怪了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.11,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.27,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一行人就在山底下的登山管理辦公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦理了今天的入山手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就可以事先對中途的中間休息站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.11,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將登山的人數姓名等資料事先發送傳真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以事先準備中飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是這個 山岳莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要在這裡住一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來比賽誰最快到達 你最好有心理準備喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐妳也是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.85,0:07:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是第一次來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做平井健一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大學參加的是登山社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都會到這裡爬山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有什麼問題可以來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要多多麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有可能就是fox啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我小蘭就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 他是我弟弟柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這是我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是從東京來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫毛利山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從關西來的 敝姓潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我跟你們一起爬山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家就好好相處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在不動產公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做什麼…跟你沒關係吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這雲的走向看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣也許會變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先打個電話到山岳莊那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小子是不是對妳有意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說fox是個慣用左手的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他從前都是用左手來射飛刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才看到的那個年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用左手的對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.90,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 我是平井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要過去打擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 您說您是毛利山先生對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是在哪裡見過面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫能勢新吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前是個小說家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是寫神秘美女記憶喪失事件的能勢新吾先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.54,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太榮幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到在這裡竟然能碰上我的讀者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你也有看過吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.08,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得裡面說的是一個喪失記憶的殺手的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的手法的確挺高明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該還沒有截止申請吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要申請入山登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的登山客還真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是很熟山裡的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.79,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟你們一塊兒走嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上還要請多照顧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都還不知道fox的特徵是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox也有可能是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是河邊 請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後大家就開始爬山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼有限的時間跟空間之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果fox要採取行動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須在山裡像遊擊隊一樣埋伏伺機而動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不然就是混在這些登山客當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.35,0:10:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們三個之外的這五個人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很有可能有一個是那個職業殺手fox
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這邊很滑大家小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請抓著繩子走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.99,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧 潮先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想害我是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條繩子是自己斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 繩子因為老舊而破破爛爛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.69,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點嚇得我老命都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是我要說的話吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這些登山客的成員裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一個是fox的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人看起來都有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個好像有點可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.72,0:11:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從剛才開始就一直張大了眼睛瞪著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.53,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的眼神好像對潮先生有什麼仇的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他本來已經領先很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然刻意的放慢等我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.11,0:11:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在談什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在觀察人類嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有 沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後一路非常順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到達了今天要住宿一個晚上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山岳莊前的最後一個休息地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我看你好有精神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常常做空手道訓練啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試試我的腳技如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個讀大學的哥哥怎麼不見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該在哪裡休息才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.25,0:12:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他八成是身份被識破了 就跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.17,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 身份被識破逃跑了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管閒事 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個人行動似乎有點可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 大家快點來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.28,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井先生怎麼會…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說就不是他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你下手的對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把他推下山去的對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放手 我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要問了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是應該趕快到下面去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他當場就死亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要隨便亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.01,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.39,0:13:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還沾了一點血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 有把刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是fox他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他的身上沒有被刺的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傷是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.10,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.36,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像是刀子劃過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那把刀子掉在那裡的狀況來看就表示…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了躲開兇手丟過去的刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不慎失足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.59,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從懸崖上面掉下來的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這是一起兇殺案嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.08,0:14:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你都去哪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少胡說八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易走到了前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他的慘叫聲以後才又回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.18,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我覺得某某人倒是比較可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你少開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們這些人攪在一起真是沒好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始所有人要到休息站去待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警方趕到這裡之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們必須跟我們一起才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你有什麼權力對我們說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了命案你們還離開現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被誤認成了兇手的話 那可就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.21,0:14:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利山先生您說話挺熟練的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您在哪裡高就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是上班族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是上班族...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光看你這個樣子也不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.51,0:15:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨越下越大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點把身體擦乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把這兒弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.08,0:15:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這個休息站的管理員嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快進來 會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚇死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 打電話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.99,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老先生 電話借用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼什麼聲音都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.82,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是剛才打的那陣雷把電話線給切斷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情常常有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在下著大雨 天又已經黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.15,0:16:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山裡到了晚上可是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要打了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這裡又是丹原山的山頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近又沒有別的休息站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們現在是完全的被孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們不是就要跟那個殺人兇手被困在這裡一整晚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個跟我們一起登山的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像出了意外一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在半路跌落山崖被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是出了意外...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.12,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手這樣弄髒這座山 太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.31,0:17:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那個犯人很有可能就在我們這間木屋裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那個人就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.70,0:17:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下有點可疑又不可疑的人就是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是推理小說常有的情節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我餓了 飯好了沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就吃這個啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家現在在山裡頭 就將就點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼不對勁呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼不對勁的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高梨先生怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被罪惡感包圍了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傢伙 這麼說果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的身上都會帶把登山刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 毛利山先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.77,0:18:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛要用假名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你在辦案子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是純粹私事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會跟這件兇殺案有關係吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這雨到底要下多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.28,0:18:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來聽聽看天氣預報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.38,0:18:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就偷偷的告訴我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著播報下一則新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上在丹原村的一位居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年六十歲的田中岩先生不幸遭人刺殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手目前很可能已經逃亡丹原山內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.63,0:19:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前有五十名警員持續在山區內搜尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣叫我怎麼睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.13,0:19:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.81,0:19:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人跑出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高梨先生不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底上哪去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 他一定是畏罪潛逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要特別小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox這次的目標可是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.87,0:20:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高梨先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.82,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 他好像不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁擠過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.71,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好他有幽閉空間恐懼症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽閉空間恐懼症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說他才會跑出休息站的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了躲雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為只要躲到這裡來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到又發作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.23,0:21:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來他就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是fox了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有過被炒房地產的人關過的經歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不肯把土地賣出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把他們給惹火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.99,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就把我關在一個很小的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你才會那麼怕房屋仲介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用你說 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.97,0:21:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.19,0:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來根本就還不知道fox是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下來這四個人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰才是殺手呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小蘭的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.85,0:22:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.82,0:22:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想對小蘭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.28,0:23:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox就在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.64,0:23:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是這個連續殺人事件的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.83,0:23:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.40,0:23:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個殺手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.88,0:23:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fox？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.26,0:23:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.51,0:23:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不僅是這個事件的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是個會把刀射出去殺人的fox的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.82,0:24:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說家能勢新吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.13,0:24:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.24,0:24:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.65,0:24:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.67,0:24:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.17,0:24:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖登山殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.58,0:24:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.98,0:24:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中小屋記帳本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.21,0:24:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回會出現嚇人的閃電跟泥石流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.99,0:24:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失戀超難過!
